= 0 C.E. --- Central Storehouses #emph[(Special)] <central-storehouses-special>
#link("#")[← Buildings & Wonders]

== Purpose <purpose>

Ancient cities relied on vast storehouses to survive poor harvests, sieges, and trade fluctuations. Grain, materials, and supplies were gathered in centralized depots controlled by the state to ensure the stability of the population.

The Central Storehouses function as a large-scale logistical hub, dramatically expanding the amount of goods your city can safely stockpile.

Once built, the Central Storehouses increase the maximum storage capacity of both your Warehouse and Granary, allowing your city to accumulate larger reserves of resources and food.

~ Strategic focus: #strong[Logistics] / #strong[economic resilience]
